{"lemma":"عُرْوَةُ","slug":"عُرْوَةُ","root":"ع.ر.#","root_slug":"ع-ر-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ر-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عُرْوَة","root":"عرو","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28881","n28882"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28881","headword_ar":"عَرْوَةٌ","root":"Erw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EarFA","text_ar":"عَرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n28882","headword_ar":"عُرْوَةٌ","root":"Erw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"primarily signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing by means of which another thing is rendered fast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"firm, and upon which reliance is placed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or it is metaphorically applied in this sense; from the same word as signifying an appertenance of a shirt, and of a mug, and of a leathern bucket. (Mgh, Msb. *) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eurowap","text_ar":"عُرْوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a shirt, (S, M, Msb,) or of a garment, (K,) is well known; (S, Msb;) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A button-loop,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loop into which a button is inserted and by means of which it is rendered fast;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing into which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~","text_ar":"زِرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"button"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereof enters;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sister of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zr~","text_ar":"زرّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurFY","text_ar":"عُرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to the copies of the K, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EariY~N","text_ar":"عَرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to some of them; and with kesr; but correctly with damm and with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"quiescent [i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurowN","text_ar":"عُرْوٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as in the Tekmileh; and also with kesr [i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EirowN","text_ar":"عِرْوٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as though these two were pls. [or rather coll. gen. ns.] of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Erwp","text_ar":"عروة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurowapN","text_ar":"عُرْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EirowapN","text_ar":"عِرْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurFY","text_ar":"عُرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ErAwY","text_ar":"عراوى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraAwaY","text_ar":"عَرَاوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurowapN","text_ar":"عُرْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is vulgar. (TA.) ―         -b3-  [The pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurFY","text_ar":"عُرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies [in like manner]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Certain"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well-known"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appertenances"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loop"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of loads, or burdens, and of the camels that bear saddles or burdens: whence the trad."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tu$ad~u AlEuraY A_il~aA A_ilaY valaAvapi masaAjida","text_ar":"لَا تُشَدُّ العُرَى اـِلَّا اـِلَى ثَلَاثَةِ مَسَاجِدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The loops"},{"kind":"text","text":"of loads"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shall not be made fast"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the purpose of journeying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"save to three mosques;"},{"kind":"text","text":"that of Mekkeh, that of El-Medeeneh, and that of El-Aksà at Jerusalem: see also similar trads. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Drb","text_ar":"ضرب"},{"kind":"text","text":"(first paragraph, see. col.,) and in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eml","text_ar":"عمل"},{"kind":"text","text":"(conj. 4)]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eurowap","text_ar":"عُرْوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the leathern bucket is likewise well known, (TA,) and so is that of the mug: (S, TA:) each is The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loopshaped"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"handle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) [so too is that of the leathern water-bag: (see 2:)] that of the mug is [also called] its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^u*un","text_ar":"اُذُن"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b5-  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eurowap","text_ar":"عُرْوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroj","text_ar":"فَرْج"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or vulva of a woman] is The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flesh of its exterior,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an external flesh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in some copies of the K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becomes, thin, and turns to the right and left, with"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the lower part of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baZor","text_ar":"بَظْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clitoris"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each of what are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurowataAni","text_ar":"عُرْوَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nymphæ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurowapN","text_ar":"عُرْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A collection of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the trees called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiDaAh","text_ar":"عِضَاه"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"those called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamoD","text_ar":"حَمْض"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are depastured in the case of drought:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or especially"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a collection of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiDaAh","text_ar":"عِضَاه"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which men pasture"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their beasts"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cattle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when they experience drought:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as remain of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiDaAh","text_ar":"عِضَاه"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamoD","text_ar":"حَمْض"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and are depastured in the case of drought;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it is not applied to any trees but these, unless to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any trees that have remained in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sayof","text_ar":"صَيْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"having survived the winter]: (TA:) also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tangled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"luxuriant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant and dense, trees, among which the camels pass the winter, and whereof they eat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and (as some say, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tree of which the leaves fall not in the winter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^araAk","text_ar":"اَرَاك"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sidor","text_ar":"سِدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trees that remain incessantly in the earth, not going:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as suffice the camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cattle, throughout the gear:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shrubs of which the lower portions remain in the earth, such as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earofaj","text_ar":"عَرْفَج"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSiY~","text_ar":"نَصِىّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the several kinds of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xul~ap","text_ar":"خُلَّة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamoD","text_ar":"حَمْض"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that when, men experience drought, the cattle gain the means of subsistence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus accord. to Az: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasture that remains after the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage has dried up;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because the cattle cling thereto, or eat thereof in the winter. ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tataEal~aqu bihaA","text_ar":"تَتَعَلَّقُ بِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and are preserved thereby: wherefore they are also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euloqap","text_ar":"عُلْقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh: [but for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealaqp","text_ar":"عَلَقة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in my copy of that work, I have substituted"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euloqap","text_ar":"عُلْقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"as being evidently the right word:]) [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqodapN","text_ar":"عُقْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the last quarter of the paragraph, in two places:] the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurFY","text_ar":"عُرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.) ―         -b7-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"environs"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a town ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where people pasture their cattle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raEayonaA Eurowapa mak~apa","text_ar":"رَعَيْنَا عُرْوَةَ مَكَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We pastured"},{"kind":"text","text":"our cattle]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the environs of Mekkeh."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b8-  And the pl.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurFY","text_ar":"عُرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A company,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, of men by whom one benefits,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"profits;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as being likened to the trees [so called] that remain [throughout the winter]: (TA:) or a company, or party, of men is likened to the trees thus called. (S.) ―         -b9-  And the sing., (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such as is held in high estimation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in much request, of camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cattle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other property;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an excel-lent horse;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eurowapu AlS~aEaAliyki","text_ar":"عُرْوَةُ الصَّعَالِيكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stay,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"support, of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SEAlyk","text_ar":"صعاليك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"needy"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and [hence] is the name [or a surname] of a well-known man. (TA. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuEoluwkN","text_ar":"صُعْلُوكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEurowapu AlwuvoqaY","text_ar":"العُرْوَةُ الوُثْقَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The firmest thing upon which one lays hold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in xxxi. 21: [see also ii. 257, where the same phrase occurs:]) and is [said to be] the saying “ There is no deity but God: ” from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEurowapu","text_ar":"العُرْوَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the first of the senses assigned to it above, as is indicated in the Msb in relation to a similar phrase here following; or] as signifying “ the trees that have a lower portion remaining in the earth, as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSiY~","text_ar":"نَصِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earofaj","text_ar":"عَرْفَج"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; ” as expl."},{"kind":"page_break","n":2029},{"kind":"text","text":"above. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awovaqu EurFY","text_ar":"اَوْثَقُ عُرًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The firmest of things upon which one lays hold"},{"kind":"text","text":"], occurring in a saying of the Prophet, is expl. as being [religious] belief, or faith. (Msb.) ―         -b12-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEurowapu","text_ar":"العُرْوَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a name of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","M","Msb","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}